	(text "To use a 2716 or 2732, place with pin 1 of\nthe chip in pin 3 of the socket.  To use a\n2716, solder across pads 1 and 2 of JP2.  To\nuse a 2732 or 2764, solder across pads 2 and\n3 of JP2 to route A11 to the socket."
